---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Custom T-Shirt Printing in Armenia | Yerevan Personal & Business Printing"
  description="High-quality custom T-shirt printing in Yerevan, Armenia. Perfect for personal designs, gifts, teams, and business branding."
>
  <main>

    <h1>Custom T-Shirt Printing in Armenia (Yerevan)</h1>

    <p>
      We print custom T-shirts for individuals, teams, and businesses.
      Suitable for both personal use and branded apparel.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>What we offer</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Custom designs and artwork printing</li>
      <li>Personal gifts and one-off shirts</li>
      <li>Team and group orders</li>
      <li>Business branding and uniforms</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Printing methods</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>DTF printing for full-color designs</li>
      <li>Silk screen printing for bulk orders</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Best for</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal custom clothing</li>
      <li>Small business branding</li>
      <li>Events and promotions</li>
      <li>Gift printing</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Advantages</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Flexible order sizes (1 to bulk)</li>
      <li>High-quality print durability</li>
      <li>Suitable for complex designs</li>
    </ul>

    <hr />

    <h2>Order Custom T-Shirts</h2>
    <p>
      Send your design, quantity, and shirt type. We will calculate price and production time.
    </p>

    <a href="/en/quote">Request a Quote</a>

  </main>
</Layout>